(5457, 316, 'pjField', 4, 'title', 'Below is a list of all routes. Routes are basic elements of the Bus Schedule system. They describe the start (departure) and the final (arrival) location of a bus trip and all intermediate stops. Here you can search, filter or sort routes. Using the arrow icon at the end of each route row you can create a reverse route or copy the selected route, which might help you in creating your routes list.', 'script'),
