(5494, 407, 'pjField', 4, 'title', 'Use the form below to start creating your bus. You need to define a route that this bus operates on and a bus type. Then you\'ll have to define departure and arrival time for each location (bus stop) along the selected route. You also have to choose which days of the week the bus is traveling and the time period this bus will operate. After saving you will be able to define the rest of the bus settings.', 'script'),
